1510
01:30:56,780 --> 01:31:00,340
♪ Someone to love is the answer

1511
01:31:00,340 --> 01:31:03,960
♪ Once you found her

1512
01:31:03,960 --> 01:31:06,080
♪ build your world around her

1513
01:31:06,700 --> 01:31:08,610
♪ Make

1514
01:31:08,610 --> 01:31:12,860
♪ someone happy

1515
01:31:12,860 --> 01:31:17,170
♪ Make just one someone happy

1516
01:31:23,620 --> 01:31:31,220
